defaultString: If by my life or death I can protect you, I will. You have my sword.

params.1: Timelessly fashionable. The helmet of a champion.
params.2: Not all who wander are lost.
params.3: A good tool improves the way you work. A great tool improves the way you think.
params.5: Ashes to ashes. Dust to dust. Bones to experience.
params.6: It is our choices that show us what we truly are. Far more than our abilities.
params.7: Go in peace in the name of Saradomin; may his glory shine upon you like the sun.
params.8: Give a noob a fish and they will leave you alone. Teach a noob to fish and they will deflate the fish market.
params.9: Life's biggest tragedy is that we get old too soon and wise too late.
params.11: Rise and rise again, until lambs become lions.
params.12: May your bloodthirst never be sated, and may all your battles be glorious. Zamorak bring you strength.
params.13: Life is a garden. You reap what you sow.
params.14: A day without laughter is a day wasted.
params.15: If by my life or death I can protect you, I will. You have my sword.
params.16: Aim steady. Perfection is unattainable, but one should always strive for it.
params.17: May you walk the path, and never fall, for Guthix walks beside thee on thy journey. May Guthix bring you peace.
params.19: Cats are easily as tough as sheep. Cats were the second thing Guthix brought here, after sheep of course.
params.21: The shield that guards the realms of men.
params.22: Brassica Prime. Thy Name be Vegetable, thy land be soil. Plant in us thy seeds of faith, that we may grow beyond allotments. Forever, your crops. Cabbage.
params.24: You must really like your clan if you put a ring on it.
params.25: A risky life, to be marked by Him. Though a skulled adventurer need not fear when their clan is near.
